  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangePasswordActivity
    Activity which displays a screen to thange the login password.
    ContactDetailsActivity
    An activity which displays a screen containing all contact details.
    ContactManagerActivity
    An activity showing a list of all contacts.
    FirstStartActivity
    This activity will be shown the first timne, the app is started.
    ListBluetoothActivity
    This activity shows all paired bluetooth devices and allows to select one of them.
    LoginActivity
    Activity which displays a login screen to the user, offering registration as well.
    MainActivity
    This activity shows the main menu of the app.
    MainPreferencesActivity
    This activity shows the preferences list.
    MainPreferencesFragment
    This fragment shows the preferences list.
    QRScanActivity
    This activity manages the key-exchange by QR-code.
    ReadSMSActivity
    This activity shows a list of all contacts with messages.
    ShowConversationActivity
    This activity shows a chosen conversation.
    SMSContactListActivity
    This activity shows all contacts.
    SMSKeyExchangeActivity
    This activity shows the screen to exchange user's key by sms.
    WriteSMSActivity
    This activity represents the message input screen.
